@architectureBaseUrl = https://localhost:5001
@middlewareBaseUrl = https://localhost:5002

### Architecture sample: list orders
GET {{architectureBaseUrl}}/orders
Accept: application/json

### Architecture sample: create order
POST {{architectureBaseUrl}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderNumber": "ORD-1003",
  "customerName": "Adventure Works",
  "totalAmount": 199.95
}

### Architecture sample: singleton clock endpoint
GET {{architectureBaseUrl}}/diagnostics/time
Accept: application/json

### Middleware sample: ping endpoint
GET {{middlewareBaseUrl}}/api/ping
Accept: application/json
